s=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲討論對錯， 係咪痴線咖"},{"pid":"87ebc1318e6fa4ba50116c097307dabd919c6bd6","tid":1470683,"uid":61520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T07:23:18.000Z","msg":"記者朋友見個依個post 唔該問番被打到腦出血， 骨折既事"},{"pid":"2ebed3b1cf78fe8f0a316ec1bbefc67c3c4a5885","tid":1470683,"uid":61520,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T07:25:31.000Z","msg":"HA secret FC左 呢個<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">唔係事實</span></strong>:<br />\n<br />\nNDH 流言澄清<br />\nFact checked from multiple primary source:<br />\n<br />\nNDH 1B / 1C Ward <br />\n冇收過cord compression<br />\n冇收過fracture femur<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">只有一位fracture humerus而且已經做左OT<br />\n</span></strong>其他既義士大多都只係neck pain<br />\n無大礙 可自由走動<br />\n<br />\n有警察有嘗試阻撓他們聯絡律師<br />\n但亦有警察都比佢地打電話<br />\n<br />\n同埋已經有人幫佢地搵左律師<br />\n但有冇見 講過啲乜<br />\n我地就不得而知⋯⋯<br />\n所以大家放心<br />\n佢地大致安好 有得食有得訓<br />\n<br />\nadmin: 請留意, 近日有人有組織及有目標地開新戰線 - 假消息戰.<br />\n<br />\n1. 制造假消息. 令到日後再有D 嚴重受傷既消息都會比人歪曲 / 質疑. <br />\n2. 放人入各group 收風 + 放流料, 互相質疑, 分化行動<br />\n3. 放人扮遊客 / 示威者, 制造畫面作文<br />\n<br />\n大家聰明既香港人, 小心唔好再亂share info.<br />\n幫手keep clean information. <br />\n今次衰左唔緊要, 我地認, 報AIRS . 下次唔好再犯, 比人利用<br />\n<br />\n另外, admin 警告作文, 消費傷者既人. <br />\n你現在同全體醫護人員作對. <br />\n依家唔係你既年代, HA Secrets 團隊有龐大網絡做fact check. 亦有大量良心同事投稿幫手fact check.<br />\n我地唔需要HAHO大台 , 我地HA Secrets 都一樣有得放消息.<br />\n<br />\n如果你打算挑戰整個醫管局, <br />\n我地會全力捍衛我地既病人.<br />\n你注定會失敗. 然後比人用完即棄.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n[url][url]<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/permalink.php?story_fbid=2286801128108595&amp;id=731331330322257&amp;__xts__[0]=68.ARB4pZXx-n3vxE-9u4dVbQsxDYXKM66ko871E7owmXBiaQNNRxZ752c9z2qwwY7SBO3AoNLLomp9HBlLgEGfKGQ0e9a_tsNHbRotEYcZtB7UQqBuXQecbgvKoYuVDw4FyWqQgD4GVmYJVajOHV8cJ70DeKRjOoXX8V5t6xpkrQ7XuTSR62CGpj6kwxddXn-8JKci6YWDbjhe1WVXXiMK2L_FwT_6Hm_za6_4FBvkcIN-MO_VRAHiqtViIFEuad_L_XXf-GVoVAUYz_QgkyzDSmcXa_Jr1SusGh5PY5pnpw58aH3Mzy6xK4oCWyB3A8FlXX0XpqU5UyAVbHQ2cGf_6A&amp;__tn__=-R[/url][/url]\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fpermalink.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D2286801128108595%26id%3D731331330322257%26__xts__%5B0%5D%3D68.ARB4pZXx-n3vxE-9u4dVbQsxDYXKM66ko871E7owmXBiaQNNRxZ752c9z2qwwY7SBO3AoNLLomp9HBlLgEGfKGQ0e9a_tsNHbRotEYcZtB7UQqBuXQecbgvKoYuVDw4FyWqQgD4GVmYJVajOHV8cJ70DeKRjOoXX8V5t6xpkrQ7XuTSR62CGpj6kwxddXn-8JKci6YWDbjhe1WVXXiMK2L_FwT_6Hm_za6_4FBvkcIN-MO_VRAHiqtViIFEuad_L_XXf-GVoVAUYz_QgkyzDSmcXa_Jr1SusGh5PY5pnpw58aH3Mzy6xK4oCWyB3A8FlXX0XpqU5UyAVbHQ2cGf_6A%26__tn__%3D-R%5B%2Furl%5D%5B%2Furl%5D&d=XnUAAdw%2Byae55KAVvns6w%2Bu9cyR3gY7uP1sO3WVLDIg%3D&h=e1c2160c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/permalink.php?story_fbid=2286801128108595&amp;id=731331330322257&amp;__xts__[0]=68.ARB4pZXx-n3vxE-9u4dVbQsxDYXKM66ko871E7owmXBiaQNNRxZ752c9z2qwwY7SBO3AoNLLomp9HBlLgEGfKGQ0e9a_tsNHbRotEYcZtB7UQqBuXQecbgvKoYuVDw4FyWqQgD4GVmYJVajOHV8cJ70DeKRjOoXX8V5t6xpkrQ7XuTSR62CGpj6kwxddXn-8JKci6YWDbjhe1WVXXiMK2L_FwT_6Hm_za6_4FBvkcIN-MO_VRAHiqtViIFEuad_L_XXf-GVoVAUYz_QgkyzDSmcXa_Jr1SusGh5PY5pnpw58aH3Mzy6xK4oCWyB3A8FlXX0XpqU5UyAVbHQ2cGf_6A&amp;__tn__=-R[/url][/url]</a>"},{"pid":"97770974d1af68860882ca2e722aeb19f4a23bc1","tid":1470683,"uid":61520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2ebed3b1cf78fe8f0a316ec